        "title": "Reacting: voi ei, harmi, kyl se siitä",
        "summary": "How Finns react to news: 'voi ei' = oh no, 'harmi' = what a shame, 'onneks' = luckily. And when things go wrong, the national motto: 'kyl se siitä' = it'll be alright, and 'ei voi mitään' = nothing to be done. Say these right and you'll sound like you grew up here.",
        "examples": [
            "Voi ei, mitä tapahtu? = Oh no, what happened?",
            "Kyl se siitä. = It'll be alright.",
            "Hienoo, onnee vaan! = Great, congrats!"
        ]
    },
